$$Q(Q(x)) = x$$

即

$$
x = 2 (2 x^2 - 1)^2 - 1
$$

因式分解为:

$$(x-1)(2x+1)(4 x^2 + 2 x - 1) = 0$$

解为$1, -\frac{1}{2}, \frac{-1 + \sqrt 5}{4}, \frac{-1 - \sqrt 5}{4}$

除去不动点$1$和$-\frac{1}{2}$, 则$\frac{-1 + \sqrt 5}{4}, \frac{-1 - \sqrt 5}{4}$为2-周期轨

经检验, $\frac{-1 + \sqrt 5}{4}, \frac{-1 - \sqrt 5}{4}$确实为2-周期轨

$$Q&#039;(x) = 4 x$$

$$|Q&#039;(\frac{-1 + \sqrt 5}{4})| = -1 + \sqrt 5 &gt; 1$$

$$|Q&#039;( \frac{-1 - \sqrt 5}{4})| = 1 + \sqrt 5 &gt; 1$$

$$Q(h(y)) = h(T(y))$$

考虑$ 0 \leq y &lt; \frac{1}{2}$, 有

$$
2h^2(y) - 1 = h(2y)
$$

容易观察

$$h(x) = \cos x$$

更一般的,

$$h(x) = \cos Ax$$

考虑$ \frac{1}{2} \leq y \leq 1$, 将$h(x) = \cos Ax$代入:

$$2 \cos^2 Ax - 1 = \cos A(2-2x) \Leftrightarrow \cos 2Ax = \cos A(2-2x) = \cos A(2x-2)$$

$$2A + 2 k \pi = 2Ax - 2A$$

取$A = \pi$

故

$$h(x) = \cos \pi x$$

$h(x)$在$[0, 1]$上是同胚的

div.data-content:
### 3

$$Q(h(y)) = h(T(y))$$

考虑$ 0 \leq y < \frac{1}{2}$, 有

$$
2h^2(y) - 1 = h(2y)
$$

容易观察

$$h(x) = \cos x$$

更一般的,

$$h(x) = \cos Ax$$

考虑$ \frac{1}{2} \leq y \leq 1$, 将$h(x) = \cos Ax$代入:

$$2 \cos^2 Ax - 1 = \cos A(2-2x) \Leftrightarrow \cos 2Ax = \cos A(2-2x) = \cos A(2x-2)$$

$$2A + 2 k \pi = 2Ax - 2A$$

取$A = \pi$

故

$$h(x) = \cos \pi x$$

$h(x)$在$[0, 1]$上是同胚的

故$Q(x)$与$T(x)$是拓扑共轭
